// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2025-0169 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: critical | ID: f44e40c5-2dca-5b81-ba24-b2ca5fecb340

#event_simpleName=*
| (ImageFileName = *debian:11* OR ImageFileName = *debian:13* OR ImageFileName = *debian:14*)
| table([timestamp, ComputerName])
| limit(1000)
